  "notes": [
    "This pilot study demonstrates a high prevalence (58.7%) of reversible tactile hypoesthesia in patients with myofascial trigger points",
    "The study suggests that trigger point injections can effectively treat both myofascial pain and associated tactile hypoesthesia",
    "The mechanism may involve inhibition of primary somatosensory cortex activity by nociceptive input from trigger points"
  ]
